<ContentLayout
  title="What Is Peaberry Coffee? The Round Bean Explained"
  description="What causes a peaberry, why only 5% of any harvest qualifies, how it roasts differently, and whether the cup quality difference is real. Plus where to buy Kona Peaberry."
  slug="learn/what-is-peaberry-coffee"
